ffectively and very importantly the quick learning required for the various disruptive solutions on the path to Digital Transformation of every customer today. \r\n\r\nI am presently looking for change from my present assignment and more importantly interested to have an opportunity to work with organisation like yours which offers Multi cloud managed services offerings, Cloud Transformation, Big Data Analytics etc where it will  be more exciting in working with different size of customers and be a implementation partner to their Digital Transformation. My relationship with large Enterprise customer and Mid sized Enterprises within TN market place can be leveraged effectively.\r\n\r\nI herewith attached my updated Resume for your kind reference and if you find me suitable, I request you to kindly let me know so that i can meet you or your relevant Head and discuss further.\r\n\";s:18:\"file-181cfdb7_file\";s:34:\"1516262176-Mohanarangan_Resume.pdf\";}', '2018-01-18 07:56:16'),
